name: Fat Kg And Snf Kg Profit Loss
query:
select 
se.custom_purchase_receipt as 'Purchase Receipt',
sed.item_code as 'Item Code',
sed.qty as 'Qty',
sed.custom_purchase_fat as 'Purchase Fat ',
sed.custom_purchase_clr as 'Purchase CLR',
sed.custom_purchase_fat_kg as 'Purchase Fat KG',
sed.custom_purchase_snf_kg as 'Purchase SNF KG',
se.name as 'Stock Entry No',
sed.custom_fat as 'Transfer Fat ',
sed.custom_clr as 'Transfer CLR',
sed.custom_fat_kg as 'Transfer Fat KG',
sed.custom_snf_kg as 'Transfer SNF KG',
sed.custom_purchase_fat_kg - sed.custom_fat_kg as ' Diff Fat KG',
sed.custom_purchase_snf_kg - sed.custom_snf_kg as ' Diff SNF KG'
from `tabStock Entry` se join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed 
on sed.parent = se.name
where
se.stock_entry_type = "Material Transfer"
AND
se.custom_fat_is_different = 1
report_name: Fat Kg And Snf Kg Profit Loss
